text: Vitaliy Raievskiy (born 12 May 1967) is a Ukrainian rower. He competed at the 1992 Summer Olympics and the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1967 births Category:Living people Category:Ukrainian male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of the Unified Team Category:Olympic rowers of Ukraine Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Zaporizhia
